# Global USE flags
# This file contains descriptions of global USE flags.
# Keep this list sorted alphabetically.

acl - Add support for Access Control Lists
alsa - Add support for the Advanced Linux Sound Architecture (ALSA)
amdgpu - Enable support for AMD GPU
apparmor - Enable support for AppArmor
assertions - Enable support for assertions
binfmt - Enable support for binfmt
blkid - Enable support for blkid
block - Enable support for block functionality
bootloader - Enable support for bootloader
bpf - Enable support for Berkeley Packet Filter
bpf-framework - Enable support for BPF framework
bsdtar - Enable support for bsdtar
bootstrap - Enable support for bootstrapping
build - Enable support for building
build-tests - Enable support for building tests
bzip2 - Add support for bzip2 compression
caps - Add support for POSIX capabilities
client - Enable support for client functionality
coredump - Enable support for coredump
cups - Add support for CUPS (Common Unix Printing System)
curl - Add support for client-side URL transfer library
dbus - Add support for D-Bus
debug - Enable extra debug codepaths, like assertions and extra output
debug-messages - Enable support for debug messages
devmode - Enable support for development mode
dhcp4 - Enable support for DHCPv4
dlang - Enable support for D language
dns - Enable support for DNS
doc - Add extra documentation (API, Javadoc, etc)
efi - Enable support for EFI
elfutils - Enable support for elfutils
examples - Install examples, usually source code
expat - Enable support for expat
fortran - Enable support for Fortran language
gcrypt - Enable support for gcrypt
gentoo-dev - Enable support for gentoo development
gentoo_repo - Enable support for gentoo repository
gprof - Enable support for gprof
gprofng - Enable support for gprofng
gshadow - Enable support for gshadow
gitweb - Enable support for gitweb
gnutls - Enable support for GnuTLS
go-bootstrap - Enable bootstrapping with Go
hostnamed - Enable support for hostnamed
hwdb - Enable support for hwdb
importd - Enable support for importd
installkernel - Enable support for installing kernel
ipc - Enable support for Inter-Process Communication
ipv6 - Add support for IP version 6
isl - Add support for Integer Set Library
jpeg - Add support for JPEG image format
keep-la - Keep libtool .la files
kmod - Enable support for kernel modules
kde - Add support for the KDE desktop environment
ldconfig - Enable support for ldconfig
ldap - Add LDAP support (Lightweight Directory Access Protocol)
libcap - Enable support for libcap
libcxx - Enable support for C++ standard library
libcxxabi - Enable support for C++ ABI library
libfuzzer - Enable support for libfuzzer
libgomp - Enable support for OpenMP with libgomp
localed - Enable support for localed
logind - Enable support for logind
logging - Enable support for logging
lua - Enable Lua scripting support
lzma - Enable support for lzma compression
machined - Enable support for machined
manpages - Install manpages
mbedtls - Enable support for mbedtls
minimal - Enable minimal build options
multicall - Enable support for multicall functionality
mpfr - Enable support for MPFR
multitarget - Enable support for multitarget functionality
natspec - Enable support for natspec
native-extensions - Enable support for native extensions
nettle - Enable support for Nettle cryptography library
networkd - Enable support for networkd
nls - Add Native Language Support (using gettext - GNU locale utilities)
nnp - Enable support for no new privileges
numa - Enable support for NUMA
nvptx - Enable support for NVPTX
oomd - Enable support for oomd
opengl - Add support for OpenGL (3D graphics)
orc - Enable support for ORC
pam - Add support for PAM (Pluggable Authentication Modules)
pcre - Add support for Perl Compatible Regular Expressions
perl - Add optional support/bindings for the Perl language
png - Add support for libpng (PNG image format)
pstore - Enable support for pstore
python - Add optional support/bindings for the Python language
qt - Enable support for Qt toolkit
readline - Enable support for libreadline
resolve - Enable support for resolve
rfkill - Enable support for rfkill
router - Enable support for router functionality
rsync-verify - Enable support for rsync verification
sanitize - Enable support for sanitizers
sanitizers - Enable support for sanitizers
savelog - Enable support for savelog
seccomp - Enable seccomp (secure computing mode) support
selinux - Enable Security Enhanced Linux support
server - Enable support for server functionality
sqlite - Add support for sqlite database
ssl - Add support for SSL/TLS connections (Secure Socket Layer / Transport Layer Security)
static - Build static libraries
static-libs - Build static versions of dynamic libraries as well
static_analyzer - Enable support for static analyzer
sysclang - Enable support for system clang
syslibcxxabi - Enable support for system libc++abi
systemd - Enable use of systemd-specific libraries and features
systemd-update - Enable support for systemd update
tempfile - Enable support for tempfile
test - Enable dependencies and/or preparations necessary to run tests (usually controlled by FEATURES=test but this flag can enable extra test code)
thermal - Enable support for thermal management
tiff - Add support for the TIFF image format
timedated - Enable support for timedated
tools - Enable support for various tools
truetype - Add support for FreeType and/or FreeType2 fonts
tui - Enable support for Text User Interface
udev - Enable install of udev rules
userdb - Enable support for userdb
user-namespaces - Enable support for user-namespaces
valgrind - Enable support for valgrind
vconsole - Enable support for vconsole
wasm - Enable support for WebAssembly
wayland - Add support for the Wayland window system
X - Add support for X11
xattr - Add support for extended attributes (filesystem)
xcore - Enable support for xcore
xdp - Enable support for XDP
xkb - Enable support for XKB
xml - Add support for XML files
xz - Add support for XZ compression
yescrypt - Enable support for yescrypt
zlib - Add support for zlib (de)compression
zstd - Add support for Zstandard compression
